import {
  Button,
  Modal,
  ModalBody,
  ModalCloseButton,
  ModalContent,
  ModalFooter,
  ModalHeader,
  ModalOverlay,
  useDisclosure,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";

export function Addtechnology({ children }) {
  const { isOpen, onOpen, onClose } = useDisclosure();
  return (
    <>
      <Button
        onClick={onOpen}
        w="32px"
        h="32px"
        bg="#212529"
        color="#FFFFFF"
        fontSize="xl"
      >
        {children}
      </Button>

      <Modal isOpen={isOpen} onClose={onClose}>
        <ModalOverlay />
        <ModalContent mt="130px" w="200px">
          <ModalHeader color="#F8F9FA" fontSize="xs" bgColor="#343B41">
            Cadastrar tecnologia
          </ModalHeader>
          <ModalCloseButton />
          <ModalBody>lala </ModalBody>

          <ModalFooter>
            <Button colorScheme="blue" mr={3} onClick={onClose}>
              Close
            </Button>
            <Button variant="ghost">Secondary Action</Button>
          </ModalFooter>
        </ModalContent>
      </Modal>
    </>
  );
}
